snippet: Honda Motor Co's CEO said he would prioritize quality improvements over the company's target of selling 6 million cars in the year starting April 2016, as the automaker recalls millions of cars to fix potentially defective air bags....

headline.print_headline: Honda CEO Says to Prioritize Quality Over Sales Target
headline.main: Honda CEO Says to Prioritize Quality Over Sales Target

lead_paragraph: Honda Motor Co's CEO said he would prioritize quality improvements over the company's target of selling 6 million cars in the year starting April 2016, as the automaker recalls millions of cars to fix potentially defective air bags.
